{"tid":2050952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"李顯龍：中國仍無法取代美國東南亞角色","createTime":"2020-06-04T12:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T12:15:39.000Z","uid":211754,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d028e816533b467c376e9de2283382fb72d44826","tid":2050952,"uid":211754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"【李顯龍：中國仍無法取代美國東南亞角色】<br />\n<br />\n新加坡總理 #李顯龍 （圖）認為，雖然中國軍事力量不斷增強，但該國在可預見的未來，還無法取代美國目前在東南亞扮演的安全方面的角色。<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍在美國《#外交事務》雜誌發表社論指出，掣肘中國的敏感因素，包括中國與區內幾個國家在南中國海有海事和領土糾紛，因此相關國家將永遠把中國海軍的出現，視為中方嘗試促進利益的舉措。<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\nlink: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Y3phgZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y3phgZ&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=02f6faaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2Y3phgZ</a>"},{"pid":"1ee833457e134bc8057dc067143ac5c910f69ff0","tid":2050952,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"管好自己個老婆先啦屌"},{"pid":"ccdb5b582c209c9be9c3c4366c3578db73531bef","tid":2050952,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:14:59.000Z","msg":"李生你老婆唔係咁講嗰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571341b638e87fa4eb7768afe7f1b597f1bc736f","tid":2050952,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"Monkey country再加入收割？"}]}